      <title>英国央行降息并暗示谨慎行事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bank-of-england-gives-hawkish-warning-as-it-cuts-rates-to-4-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行官员决定将利率降至19个月低点，其中两位官员支持大幅降息50个基点，促使市场加大对进一步宽松政策的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bank-of-england-gives-hawkish-warning-as-it-cuts-rates-to-4-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 12:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
